reject socialism, reject

00:05:16.190 --> 00:05:21.280
collectivism, and
go with the gut.

00:05:21.280 --> 00:05:24.380
We even have a chapter
just on food.

00:05:24.380 --> 00:05:29.090
Why America is the crispest,
crunchiest, most corn-fed

00:05:29.090 --> 00:05:30.190
nation on earth.

