00:05:53.720 --> 00:05:56.260
I mean everybody's got their
top, like what their top 10

00:05:56.260 --> 00:05:56.300
amendments are.

00:05:56.300 --> 00:05:59.210
ERIC SCHMIDT: Do you have
a top you like?

00:05:59.210 --> 00:05:59.996
STEPHEN COLBERT: My number
one would probably

00:05:59.996 --> 00:06:01.970
be the Second Amendment.

00:06:01.970 --> 00:06:04.273
And my number two
would probably

00:06:04.273 --> 00:06:06.100
be the First Amendment.

00:06:06.100 --> 00:06:08.730
And then probably my third
would be the Seventh.

00:06:08.730 --> 00:06:10.180
My fourth would be the 10th.

00:06:10.180 --> 00:06:11.996
Fifth would be the Ninth.

00:06:11.996 --> 00:06:13.270
Sixth would be the Eighth.

00:06:13.270 --> 00:06:14.480
