[INTERPOSING VOICES]

00:06:30.200 --> 00:06:31.670
STEPHEN COLBERT: The Second
Amendment allows

00:06:31.670 --> 00:06:33.300
this book to exist.

00:06:33.300 --> 00:06:33.510
ERIC SCHMIDT: The First
Amentment--

00:06:33.510 --> 00:06:35.100
STEPHEN COLBERT: Because if
anybody stopped-- no, no, the

